'''阿彼锡·巴克罕'''（अभिषेक बच्चन，Abhishek Bachchan，{{bd|1976年|2月5日|catIdx=Bachchan, Abhishek}}，又可译为'''阿彼錫·巴沙坎'''或'''阿彼锡·巴克强'''），他是[[印度|印度]][[宝莱坞|宝莱坞]]的著名男演员[[阿米塔巴·巴沙坎|阿米塔巴·巴沙坎]]之子。

== 生平==
他出生于孟买，是演员[[阿米塔巴·巴沙坎|阿米塔巴·巴沙坎]]和[[贾雅·巴克罕|贾雅·巴克罕]]之子，有一个姐姐[[舒维塔·巴克罕·南达|舒维塔·巴克罕·南达]]<ref>{{cite news |last1=Raghuvanshi |first1=Aakanksha |title=Basant Panchami: Why Amitabh Bachchan's Throwback Pic With Baby Abhishek Is Special |url=https://www.ndtv.com/entertainment/basant-panchami-why-amitabh-bachchans-throwback-pic-with-baby-abhishek-is-special-2171344 |access-date=15 February 2021 |work=NDTV |date=29 January 2020 |archive-date=2022-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220118212201/https://www.ndtv.com/entertainment/basant-panchami-why-amitabh-bachchans-throwback-pic-with-baby-abhishek-is-special-2171344 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9岁时，他确诊[[难语症|难语症]]<ref>{{Cite news|last=Alves|first=Glynda|url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/magazines/panache/these-celebs-dont-let-their-disabilities-hold-them-back/articleshow/45120460.cms|title=These celebs don't let their disabilities hold them back|date=12 November 2014|work=The Economic Times|access-date=21 February 2020|archive-date=2022-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220118051505/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/magazines/panache/these-celebs-dont-let-their-disabilities-hold-them-back/articleshow/45120460.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.timesnownews.com/health/article/abhishek-bachchan-struggled-with-dyslexia-as-a-child-signs-and-symptoms-your-child-is-dyslexic-causes-treatment/377635|title=Abhishek Bachchan was diagnosed with dyslexia at age 9: All you need to know about this learning disorder|website=www.timesnownews.com|language=en|access-date=21 February 2020|date=6 March 2019|archive-date=2022-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119000342/https://www.timesnownews.com/health/article/abhishek-bachchan-struggled-with-dyslexia-as-a-child-signs-and-symptoms-your-child-is-dyslexic-causes-treatment/377635|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在孟买和新德里读高中后，就读瑞士[[艾格隆学院|艾格隆学院]]<ref>[http://indianexpress.com/photos/entertainment-gallery/happy-birthday-abhishek-bachchan-jr-turns-38/#abhi3 Happy Birthday Abhishek! Bachchan Jr. turns 38] {{Wayback|url=http://indianexpress.com/photos/entertainment-gallery/happy-birthday-abhishek-bachchan-jr-turns-38/#abhi3 |date=20140214125908 }}. ''The Indian Express''</ref>，之后又进入[[波士顿大学|波士顿大学]]，但没有获得学位便进入[[宝莱坞|宝莱坞]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bollywoodmantra.com/news/bollywood-stars-who-lived-abroad/9060/ |title=Bollywood Stars Who Lived Abroad |publisher=Bollywoodmantra.com |date=30 May 2012 |access-date=9 January 2013 |archive-date=2012-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120804233332/http://www.bollywoodmantra.com/news/bollywood-stars-who-lived-abroad/9060/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.jamactors.com/jamactors/abhishekbachchan.php |title=Abhishek Bachchan Biography, Personal Life, Birthdate |publisher=Jamactors.com |access-date=11 June 2013 |archive-date=2013-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131212052202/http://www.jamactors.com/jamactors/abhishekbachchan.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 个人生活 ==
2006年中，印度[[传媒|传媒]]开始猜测阿彼锡与同是天后巨星级的[[宝莱坞|宝莱坞]]女演员[[爱絲維娅莉|艾西瓦娅·莉]]之间的不一般亲密关系。阿彼锡当时和艾西瓦娅在拍摄电影《Umrao Jaan》期间相恋。<ref>[https://www.ndtv.com/entertainment/umrao-jaan-is-very-special-to-me-abhishek-bachchan-on-film-where-it-all-began-with-wife-aishwarya-2248226?amp=1&akamai-rum=off “"Umrao Jaan Is Very Special To Me": Abhishek Bachchan On Film Where It All Began With Wife Aishwarya”] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ndtv.com/entertainment/umrao-jaan-is-very-special-to-me-abhishek-bachchan-on-film-where-it-all-began-with-wife-aishwarya-2248226?amp=1&akamai-rum=off |date=20200713110610 }} NDTV [18-06-2020]</ref>2007年初，两人终于向外界宣告[[订婚|订婚]]。4月21日，兩大[[寶萊塢|寶萊塢]]巨星舉行盛大的[[婚禮|世紀婚禮]]，此举哄動印度全国，數以萬計群眾在[[孟買|孟買]]争睹新人并向他们祝福。

按照计划，婚后的[[艾西瓦娅·巴克罕|艾西瓦娅·巴克罕]]将退出影坛，做一个传统的印度[[家庭|家庭]]式女性。而阿比锡既得到了很多[[影迷|影迷们]]的祝福，也因为征服了号称「全球最美丽女士」的芳心，被无数心怀妒忌的男士们冠以“那个幸运的小骗子”（The Lucky Dupe）之不雅[[绰号|绰号]]。

2020年，印度爆發[[2019冠狀病毒病印度疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]。7月11日，阿彼锡的父亲阿米塔布在社交媒體上表示自己被確診感染了[[2019冠狀病毒病|2019冠狀病毒病]]。阿彼锡也在同日确诊。<ref>[https://metro.co.uk/2020/07/11/bollywood-star-amitabh-bachchan-tests-positive-coronavirus-12977336/ "Bollywood star Amitabh Bachchan hospitalised for coronavirus as son Abhishek tests positive"] {{Wayback|url=https://metro.co.uk/2020/07/11/bollywood-star-amitabh-bachchan-tests-positive-coronavirus-12977336/ |date=20210405031020 }} Metro UK [11-07-2020]</ref>同月12日，他的妻子艾西瓦娅和女儿阿拉迪雅也正式确诊。<ref>[https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/jul/12/aishwarya-rai-bachchan-tests-positive-for-coronavirus-india-actor-amitabh “Aishwarya Rai Bachchan tests positive for coronavirus“] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/jul/12/aishwarya-rai-bachchan-tests-positive-for-coronavirus-india-actor-amitabh |date=20200717142500 }} The Guardian [12-07-2020]</ref><ref>[https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-53380291 "Coronavirus: Three generations of Bollywood Bachchan family infected"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-53380291 |date=20210405030957 }} BBC [12-7-2020]</ref>8月8日，他康复出院。<ref>[https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/abhishek-bachchan-discharged-from-hospital-coronavirus-negative-6545955/ {{Wayback|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/abhishek-bachchan-discharged-from-hospital-coronavirus-negative-6545955/ |date=20210218042427 }} “Abhishek Bachchan discharged from hospital, Amitabh Bachchan thanks well wishers” The Indian Express [08-08-2020]</ref>

